author: Unreal Engine
description:
Unreal Engine 5.7 empowers you to build expansive, lifelike, high-performance worlds filled with rich, beautifully detailed dense vegetation; author and render physically accurate layered and blended materials with true visual fidelity; and light complex worlds like never before. 

You’ll also experience smoother and more intuitive animation and rigging workflows—all while getting instant guidance along the way from the new in-editor UE AI Assistant.

Discover more of what's new in Unreal Engine 5.7
